eties Save me from the Fire that shall break my bones, burn my body, and destroy my strength. O God! Please bless me with the perseverance of the Household of Muhammad. Please establish me as one of those awaiting their Rule Please establish me as their helpers and supporters in this world and the Hereafter.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ يَا مُجَلِّيَ عَظَاۗئِمِ الْهُمُوْمِ جَلِّ عَنِّيْ هَمَّةَ الْهُمُوْمِ وَاَجِرْنِيْ مِنْ نَارٍ تَقْصِمُ عِظَامِيْ وَتُحْرِقُ اَحْشَاۗئِيْ وَتُفَرِّقُ قُوَايَ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ ارْزُقْنِيْ صَبْرَ آلِ مُحَمَّدٍ وَاجْعَلْنِيْ اَنْتَظِرُ اَمْرَهُمْ وَاجْعَلْنِيْ مِنْ اَنْصَارِهِمْ وَاَعْوَانِهِمْ فِي الدُّنْيَا وَالْآخِرَةِ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14"